    "en": {
      "title": "47 smugglers arrested",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Navy said that 47 persons were arrested in the seas off Negombo for attempting to cross into Australia illegally on a multi-day trawler.",
        "Among the group were 34 men, 06 women and 07 children, the Navy said.",
        "The suspects are aged between 1 and 50 and are residents of Jaffna, Kilinochchi, Mannar, Wennappuwa, Chilaw and Batticaloa."
      ],
